Projectify is a [[TiddlyWiki|https://tiddlywiki.com]] plugin for managing projects & todo lists, inspired by projects such as [[Todoist|https://todoist.com]] and [[Basecamp|https://basecamp.com]]. It is released under the MIT license.

For all changes in the latest {{$:/plugins/nico/projectify!!version}} release, see [[ChangeLog|$:/plugins/nico/projectify/changelog]].

